        "timestamp": "2017-08-07 15:18:02.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2: Code-Review+2\n\nThis is step 1 of 2 in what I hope is a permanent fix to our missing versions problem.  In this change, I am doing 2 things:\n1) Adding new parent pom artifactIds that reflect the ODL release they should be used with.  Left the existing \"root\" artifactId there for backward compatibility.\n2) Updated sync-core root pom to use version 1.1.0 of the old root pom (can't use new ones yet because they don't exist - so the top level sdnc core pom.xml compile would fail",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
